@{b}@{u}Test Access Pinouts@{uu}@{ub}

 Type: All Cases 10-way solder buckets (no header)

+-----+------------------------+---------------------+---------------------+
| Pin |     TP1 Pinout         |   TP2 Pinout        |   TP3 Pinout        |
+-----+------------------------+---------------------+---------------------+
|     |                        |                     |                     |
|  1  | CPU Clock              | Colour Clock        | _DBR                |
|  2  | _Address Strobe        | Colour Clock Quad.  | Register Addr Bus 8 |
|  3  | _Data Strobe           | _RAM Enable         | Register Addr Bus 7 |
|  4  | Processor Read/Write   | _Chip Register Enabl| Register Addr Bus 6 |
|  5  | _Data Send Ack. 0      | _Blitter Slowdown   | Register Addr Bus 5 |
|  6  | _Data Send Ack. 1      | _OEB                | Register Addr Bus 4 |
|  7  | _ROM Enable            | _Row Addr. Strobe   | Register Addr Bus 3 |
|  8  | _CDIS                  | _Col Addr. Strobe   | Register Addr Bus 2 |
|  9  | _Keyboard Reset        | _DWE                | Register Addr Bus 1 |
| 10  | Ground                 | Ground              | Ground              |
+-----+------------------------+---------------------+---------------------+


It is highly unadvisable to actually use these unless you know what you are
doing. Make sure you have the right end of the row for starters!
