                    CPU:  68RC040
    Manufactured Speeds:  25MHz
        FPU Socket Type:  FPU built-in
     No of SIMM Sockets:  1 x 72pin  ( accepts all 72pin variants 
                                       eg  Non-Parity - Parity - EDO )
